description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Parvati purrs with a rating of 74, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 148, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 3 for East, Nine Lives for South, and Stringalong for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40742-13972-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
